    "content": "<div class=\"noinclude\"><span class=\"breadcrumbs xulRefAttr_breadcrumbs\">Â« <a href=\"/en-US/docs/XUL/XUL_Reference\">XUL Reference home</a></span></div>\n\n<dl>\n <dt><code id=\"a-closemenu\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/Attribute/closemenu\">closemenu</a></code></dt>\n <dd>Type: <em>one of the values below</em></dd>\n <dd>Indicates if the menu closes when the <code>menuitem</code> is activated.</dd>\n <dd>\n <dl>\n  <dt><code>auto</code></dt>\n  <dd>This, the default value if the <code>closemenu</code> attribute is not specified, closes up the menu and all parent menus.</dd>\n  <dt><code>single</code></dt>\n  <dd>The menu the item is contained within is closed, but the parent menus remain open.</dd>\n  <dt><code>none</code></dt>\n  <dd>No menus are closed.</dd>\n </dl>\n </dd>\n</dl>",
